              <Comments>See {S:04100700400012} apparatus.|There is some doubt as to the precise extent to which {L:βαπτίζω&lt;SDBG:βαπτίζω:000000&gt;}[a], καταβαπτίζω, and {L:βαπτισμός&lt;SDBG:βαπτισμός:000000&gt;}[a] in {S:04100700400012} involve ritual cleansing, but the context would seem to imply this, particularly in view of the relationship of such washing to the rules followed by Jews in general and Pharisees in particular.</Comments>
